### LMS API Requests (use VS Code REST Client)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@json = Content-Type: application/json

### Register
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
{{json}}

{
  "name": "Karthik Instructor",
  "email": "karthik@centennialcollege.ca",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "instructor"
}

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
{{json}}

{
  "email": "karthik@centennialcollege.ca",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Me
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create Course (as instructor)
POST {{baseUrl}}/courses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
{{json}}

{
  "title": "LMS-G2",
  "description": "React LMS App"
}

### List Courses
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses

### Enroll as student (login student first to get token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/enrollments
Authorization: Bearer {{studentToken}}
{{json}}

{
  "courseId": "<courseId>"
}

### Admin list users
GET {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
